{"tid":1098705,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"康文署又勝一仗","createTime":"2019-04-09T08:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T12:20:21.000Z","uid":167573,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b50584fd4a84ccbe448824fd414443a80edc6f5c","tid":1098705,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T08:52:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">演唱會一票難求，黃牛飛問題猖獗惹關注</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員劉國勳今(9日)引述消息稱<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">康文署將推新招打擊，今年7月起，在香港體育館及伊利沙伯體育館舉辦連續4場或以上活動，內部認購與公開發售比例，將由目前的8:2修改至7:3。</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n劉歡迎決定，但認為比例仍屬保守及未有推動實名制，建議活動場數愈多，公開發售比例要愈高。他亦促請當局交出修例時間表，且提高罰則。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他今午1時至2時曾嘗試登入城市電腦售票網購票，但一直未能進入網站，因此他促請當局改善有關電腦系統，否則即使調整售票比例，市民亦只能望門興嘆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190409/bkn-20190409152129417-0409_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190409%2Fbkn-20190409152129417-0409_00822_001.html&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLYyfatP4vaZW2FmQrzE7DSA%3D&h=053a27ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190409/bkn-20190409152129417-0409_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"dcb7755b9cfd8e691e23124edf9783e19445730d","tid":1098705,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"推番上去先～"}]}